node.text:
Let's keep moving to stay physically and mentally healthy!
Congrats to our Uber Energy Drink PS5 giveaway winners! Get an extra boost to get through the rest of your day. 👉🏼 @uberenergydrinkusa and @uberenergydrinkofficial

Uber Energy Drink PS5 giveaway winner list:
@shrey.gupta.26 , @ryan_fauble & @dredstanleywilder.
Winners will receive a DM from us this week.
